//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0001>"(Alright.)"
<enT0001>"(Alright.)"

//TEXT
<jaT0002>I thought it might be more effective to slice up that shapeless foe, so I pulled my combat knife from its sheath. I ran over to the jelly creature and swung down with all my might.
<enT0002>I thought it might be more effective to slice up that shapeless foe, so I pulled my combat knife from its sheath. I ran over to the jelly creature and swung down with all my might.

//TEXT
<jaT0003>I cut in two with a single stroke. Or so I expected, but luck was against me. There was no response at all. In fact, things took a turn for the worse.
<enT0003>I cut in two with a single stroke. Or so I expected, but luck was against me. There was no response at all. In fact, things took a turn for the worse.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0004>"Gah! What's this? It leaped onto my arm!"
<enT0004>"Gah! What's this? It leaped onto my arm!"

//TEXT
<jaT0005>As if its slow movement was a complete lie, it leapt with great agility the instant my hand neared it. It coiled itself around my arm and starting pulling as if it were dragging me inside itself.
<enT0005>As if its slow movement was a complete lie, it leapt with great agility the instant my hand neared it. It coiled itself around my arm and starting pulling as if it were dragging me inside itself.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0006>"No, Shuhei-kun!"
<enT0006>"No, Shuhei-kun!"

//TEXT
<jaT0007>I leapt back when I heard Nao's scream but ... something unbelievable happened. My arm, turned light brown as if it had underwent necrosis, popped off and landed on the floor.
<enT0007>I leapt back when I heard Nao's scream but ... something unbelievable happened. My arm, turned light brown as if it had underwent necrosis, popped off and landed on the floor.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0008>"My, my arm..."
<enT0008>"My, my arm..."

//TEXT
<jaT0009>Stunned, I tried to get back. However...
<enT0009>Stunned, I tried to get back. However...

//TEXT
<jaT0010>The next second, my sight was squashed shut.
<enT0010>The next second, my sight was squashed shut.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0011>"(What is this? It doesn't hurt, and there's no blood... but my strength is quickly leaving my body...)"
<enT0011>"(What is this? It doesn't hurt, and there's no blood... but my strength is quickly leaving my body...)"

//TEXT
<jaT0012>Unable to stand, my knees fell to the floor. I desperately tried to rise, but that was too difficult and my hands fell to the floor. I had collapsed.
<enT0012>Unable to stand, my knees fell to the floor. I desperately tried to rise, but that was too difficult and my hands fell to the floor. I had collapsed.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0013>"(Dammit... If I collapse here, what'll happen to Nao. Get it together, Shuhei!)"
<enT0013>"(Dammit... If I collapse here, what'll happen to Nao. Get it together, Shuhei!)"

//TEXT
<jaT0014>I grinded my teeth in disappointment with myself, but my body would no longer move by my will. Just barely, I could hear sounds... but...
<enT0014>I grinded my teeth in disappointment with myself, but my body would no longer move by my will. Just barely, I could hear sounds... but...

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0015>"Shuhei-kun, Shuhei-kun...."
<enT0015>"Shuhei-kun, Shuhei-kun...."

//TEXT
<jaT0016>It felt far away. I could hear Nao crying as my consciousness slowly left my body.
<enT0016>It felt far away. I could hear Nao crying as my consciousness slowly left my body.

